  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nStar Atlas Surge Technical Test\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about the Star Atlas Surge test.\nMetaverse Nomads #140 w/ Star Atlas Starbased – April 2nd Release\nMetaverse Nomads posted a replay of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nSTAR ATLAS #227 Big Changes You Need To Know! DONT LOSE MONEY!\nMetaverse Explorer posted a video with updates in Star Atlas.\nA NEW ECONOMIC PARADIGM\nAephia published an article about the economy changes in Star Atlas.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #123\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nStar Atlas – Surge Trailer\nStar Atlas released a trailer for their Surge game mode.\nStar Atlas “Surge” Gameplay Reveal! + Starbased Launch! CEO INTERVIEW\nPaul Barron Network had an interview with Star Atlas CEO Michael Wagner.\n20 | STARBASED is FINALLY HERE!!! | Star Atlas\nPathfinder posted a video about the release of Star Atlas SAGE Starbased.\nThe Atlas Brew #105\nStar Atlas TV posted a recording of the latest Atlas Brew.\nStar Atlas: Starbased Walkthrough Tutorial\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video walkthrough of some parts of Starbased.\nStar Atlas Star Based Game Play! Don’t make this mistake\nOCG Thor posted a video about a mistake he made in SAGE Starbased.\nSTARBASED – THE MISSING MANUAL!\nAephia published an article with information about Starbased.\nAtlas Brew #105: Starbased – TLDR\nBeth posted a video recapping the latest Atlas Brew.\nSTAR ATLAS GAMEPLAY – STARBASED [ FIRST IMPRESSIONS ]\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video of his first impressions of SAGE Starbased.",
